data.description: Don’t miss the opportunity to call this beauty…home in one of the most desired areas. This is a one owner home that’s been well taken care. The home offers an open concept and split floor plan. As you walk in, you are met by a beautiful formal living room space, but could be used as a formal dining area too. The entryway leading to the rest of the home is open and  complemented by tons of natural sunlight, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation. The heart of the home is the kitchen. It is well-equipped with double ovens, built in microwave, dishwasher, walk in pantry, plenty of cabinets, breakfast bar and offers a spacious open layout that includes the dining area and living room. There are three spacious bedrooms and 4th room could be an office, flex room, or another bedroom if needed. The rear patio and large backyard offer plenty of space for family activities & hosting special occasions. The house's overall design creates a serene ambiance, making it a perfect retreat to call home. Centrally located to the YMCA, walking trails, dog park, shopping and so much more.
